evidence.claim: Lakechief adheres to HIPAA regulations for health data security and privacy.
The company employs HL7 standards for interoperability in health data exchange.
Lakechief utilizes AWS for its cloud infrastructure to ensure scalable service delivery.
They mention using integration patterns in their developer docs for seamless data interaction.
Lakechief's career page indicates a focus on engineering talent for platform development involving health tech solutions.
